ActHealth of Animals Act
PrecisRegulations Amending the HEALTH OF ANIMALS REGULATIONS AND THE REGULATIONS AMENDING CERTAIN REGULATIONS ADMINISTERED AND ENFORCED BY THE CANADIAN FOOD INSPECTION AGENCY which bring the import requirements related to the control of Bovine Spongiform Encephalopathy (BSE) for animals and related products originating in the United States in line with those applicable to other countries.
